languages.text: "Что... что... они идут из темноты, и крадут свет... тьма ненасытна... за ними, за крадущими следом неведомое око, оно смотрит, смотрит... ааа!"

"What... what... they're coming out of the darkness, they're stealing the light... the darkness is insatiable... and behind them, behind these thieves, an ineffable eye follows, watching, watching... aargh!"

languages.text: « Que... que... elles sortent des ténèbres, elles volent la lumière... les ténèbres sont insatiables... et derrière elles, derrière ces voleuses, un œil ineffable suit, observe, observe... aargh ! »

languages.text: “什么……那是什么……他们从黑暗中出现，偷走了光明……黑暗永不满足……在他们的背后，在那些小偷的背后，有一只无法形容的眼睛在注视着……注视着……啊啊啊！”
languages.original_text: "What... what... they're coming out of the darkness, they're stealing the light... the darkness is insatiable... and behind them, behind these thieves, an ineffable eye follows, watching, watching... aargh!"

languages.text: 「なっ…なっ…暗闇から現れて、光を奪う…暗闇はとどまるところを知らない…そしてその後ろ、盗人の背後で、なんとも言えない目が付いてきて、見てる、見てる…ああぁっ！」

languages.text: «Qué... qué... están saliendo de la oscuridad, están robando la luz... la oscuridad es insaciable... y detrás de ellos, detrás de estos ladrones, un ojo inefable les sigue, observando, vigilando... ¡aargh!».

languages.text: "Ne... Ne... Karanlıktan çıkıyor, ışığı gasbediyorlar... Karanlık doymak bilmiyor... Bu hırsızların tam arkasında tarif edilemez gözler bakıyor, izliyor, izliyor... Ah!"
